        "composition"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，组合关系用实心菱形。那Bomb类需要哪些属性和方法？我注意到您提到\"效果\"，具体是什么类型？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bomb",
        "effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Bomb有一个私有属性effect，类型用double，表示爆炸强度。构造方法是无参的Bomb()，再加上一个fire()方法返回void，用来执行爆炸。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bomb",
        "effect",
        "double",
        "Bomb()",
        "fire()"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Bomb类结构清楚了。那Tick类呢？它需要维护当前累计时间吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Tick",
        "sum"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Tick有一个私有int类型的sum记录累计滴答次数。构造方法Tick(int)接收初始值。关键方法是tick()，每次调用返回boolean表示是否触发爆炸。另外Tick内部要持有Bomb实例，字段名就叫bomb。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Tick",
