      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我画好了：Tick通过组合关联包含Bomb，多重性是一对一。Bomb的effect是private double，Tick的sum是private int，bomb字段也是private。方法签名都按您说的标注了。您看一下结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
